    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab> Die iovis, VII kal. agusti, in claustro <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/53">Sancti
                            Sisti</orgName>. <persName>Ercarius Ferrarius</persName> et
                            <persName>Robertus filii</persName> quondam <persName
                            >Roberti Ferrarii</persName> atque <persName>Iohannes</persName>
                        et <persName>Gerardus Obertus</persName> atque <persName
                            >Bernardus Ferrarius</persName> inter se consentientes fecerunt finem et
                        datum domino <persName key="#Abbots" ref="people/16"
                            >Gandulfo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs> Sancti Sisti de <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >XXV iugeris terre</rs> posite ad <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Purchase"
                            ref="#places/14"><geogName
                                ref="#estates/76"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Purchase"
                                >Cotreviam</geogName></placeName> que ab eodem monesterio tenebant.
                        Gerardus vero et Obertus Iohannes et Bernardus fecerunt hanc finem quia
                        receperunt <rs key="#Feudum">cambium de feudo</rs> eorum comuni quod tenent
                            <rs key="#Local_elites">a dominis de Arcellis</rs>, nominatim pro his
                        XXV iugeris ab Ercario et Roberto Ferrario. Et pro hac fine Ercarius et
                        Robertus acceperunt a domino Gandulfo CXVI libras Placentinas. Actum cum
                        stipulatione anno MCXC, indictione VIII. Testes: <persName key="#witness"
                            >Obertus filius domini Oberti de Porta</persName>, <persName
                            >magister Petrus de Castro Arquato</persName>, <persName
                            >Pelegrinus de Marracio</persName>, <persName>Carpinus</persName>
                        et <persName>Gualengus Belengarius</persName>. <persName
                            key="#notary">Petrus Lachetta</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs></ab>
                </div>
            </div>
